# Deployment

## Docker

```bash
docker build \
  --build-arg VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://aireview.com \
  --build-arg VITE_USE_MOCK_API=false \
  -t meridian-web:latest .
```

Runtime config is written to `/config.json` by `docker-entrypoint.sh` from env vars:
`API_BASE_URL`, `API_RANK_PATH`, `USE_MOCK_API`.

## Kubernetes

```bash
kubectl apply -f k8s/configmap.yaml
kubectl apply -f k8s/deployment.yaml
kubectl apply -f k8s/service.yaml
kubectl apply -f k8s/ingress.yaml
```

Health probe: `GET /health`. Update `k8s/ingress.yaml` host and TLS secret for your domain.

## Production checklist

- Set `USE_MOCK_API=false` in ConfigMap
- Point `API_BASE_URL` to live backend (`https://aireview.com`)
- Ensure backend CORS allows the frontend origin
- Build image in CI and push to your container registry
